say.description: Say a message as the server.

lua.description: Execute Lua, return the desired reply.

unmute.description: Allow a muted player to talk

ban.description: Ban a player from the session

status.description: Lists all the players on the server with their ids and basic information on the server

uptime.description: Get the uptime of the server

about.description: Displays the license, version, and copyright notice assosiated with Cobalt Essentials.

togglechat.description: Toggles viewing chat in the RCON client

help.description: Lists all commands accessible by the player

statusdetail.description: Lists all the players on the server in detail along with basic server information
